{"tid":1590893,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"打破國外企業壟斷 國內最大規模晶圓生產廠投產 量產8英吋晶圓？！","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T05:20:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"69a06927c72a5b7b1adb64c2bc85fbd396364828","tid":1590893,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:45:37.000Z","msg":"據報道，杭州中欣晶圓半導體股份有限公司大晶圓(硅片）項目21日在杭州錢塘新區竣工投產，實現了8英吋晶圓的正式量產，同時12英吋大晶圓生產線進入調試、試生產階段。<br />\n<br />\n據瞭解，國內大尺寸晶圓尤其是12英吋半導體大晶圓的供應長期被國外企業所掌控，市場高度壟斷。這一項目的建成投產，將改變國內半導體大晶圓完全依賴國外的現狀，有效填補國內半導體大晶圓供應的行業短板，有助於推動我國集成電路產業發展。預計這一項目明年將實現月產35萬枚8英吋半導體大晶圓。12英吋半導體晶圓生產線投產後，月產能將達3萬片，將大大緩解我國半導體大晶圓供應不足的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.jrj.com.cn/madapter/stock/2019/09/23082028165600.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.jrj.com.cn%2Fmadapter%2Fstock%2F2019%2F09%2F23082028165600.shtml&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=bdd368f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.jrj.com.cn/madapter/stock/2019/09/23082028165600.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"1eccdd09fc0ed37efeb834805428b0fbc59a6aff","tid":1590893,"uid":72000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"又係外國撻啲技術返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3b44943a16fd9ff43fd9a9dfbe6c1ab55c4404","tid":1590893,"uid":43558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"連咩 feature size 都冇講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你開多條12英吋做 14nm 28nm 呢啲就唔好話打破國外壟斷<br />\n人地 TSMC 下年量產 5nm 喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b2ea5019b7f6eff9344b2c8a89d70eda882868","tid":1590893,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"優良率0% 有撚用咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}